Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:36.45,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(1070,178)}燈火管制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}里克  里克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}吶 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫的這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃... 那是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的~ 都無所謂啦~ 快點穿上衣服~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去把大家叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她也漂流到這島上了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個掛墜是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}散發出像彩虹色的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得有種神秘的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那人倒在海灘上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亞蜜露呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去診所叫隆醫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隆醫生 還有的救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瞧呀... 這可真是美麗的掛墜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鑲嵌著從未看過的寶石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}醫生  掛墜什麼的都無所謂啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然沒有生命危險的跡象 但是體溫很低啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之先把她送到診所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能幫忙一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.99,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\bord3\fad(450,0)\blur8\pos(644,622)}— 診所 —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是意識還沒恢復 照現在這個樣子啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許這段時間都是這個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們快去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果恢復意識的話 會馬上通知你們的啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果擔心的話 隨時都可以過來看她的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是像她一樣漂流過來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為里克是穿著鎧甲的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把你扶起來或是陪著你一起走都是很累人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦~ 再不快點回到店裡的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點回去一起做麵包吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一、二~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點~ 快點~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們跑的太快了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:54.14,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\fad(450,400)\blur8\pos(635,616)}— 麵包坊　魯·克魯 —
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是竟然又有一個人漂流過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克也是在這種暴風雨中漂過來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼穿著那種鎧甲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克明明只適合圍裙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對啊~ 對啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能幫我看一下後面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爐子的溫度上不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨的時候折斷了 堵在那裡了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是如果這樣的話 那把樹枝拿出來不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像以前爐子就有點裂痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨那天 雨水好像就順著樹枝流進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爐子裡積水太多 裂痕變得更嚴重了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是導致每天烤爐溫度這麼高的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是因為高溫瞬間冷卻的關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個烤爐原本就很重 有一個地方壞了的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}承受不住重量 就會像那樣壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實之前有段時間 里克說過爐子的溫度不好控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊... 近期無法營業了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:55.47,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(630,625)}— 馬黛拉麵包坊 —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}本來想拜託小鎮上的鐵匠修理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}不過他們也忙不過來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是暴風雨過後 工作增加了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}修理麵包爐的話 去找住在山裡的漢克也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在矮人族裡脾氣也是古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}技術是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}矮人族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 能在借用一下馬車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 儘管用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:36.01,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(644,623)}— 漢克的工坊 —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}漢克先生在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 我們的石爐在暴風雨中壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能幫忙修理嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}修理費要提前全額支付
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 現在錢還沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且你先來看一下爐子的樣子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種事不看也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}憑著多年的經驗也猜得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且是第一次的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有像你們這樣的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我有什麼理由相信你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在多多拜託一下漢克先生 說不定就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們沒帶足錢是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且漢克說的也有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有 既然爐子不能馬上就修好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要考慮下每天怎麼做麵包了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天酵母都已經浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不開始做麵包的話也賺不到修爐子的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來歷不明的大船正在接近小島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來以為是暴風雨裡的遇害船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對方也好像沒有求救的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定是海盜船的偵查部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海盜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個島上也有自稱是海盜的人出現在小酒館裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們的工作是尋找財寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是也有一部分人做著搶劫和販賣人口的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是傷害別人的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要是值錢的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管是人還是財物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是群危險的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼今天晚上...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該會進行久違的燈火管制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}燈火管制？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼晚上在屋子裡也不能點燈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來會是個寂靜的夜晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為來歷不明的大船接近 實行燈火管制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晚上禁止外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要趕快準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 燈火管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}工作就先做到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能點燈的話飯也做不成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等待你們麵包的人肯定很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們幾個在天黑之前要把麵包送到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Hi~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來送麵包了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~ 請拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個 雖然晚了點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是今天外送麵包的份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為沒外出採購 食物就要吃完了 正苦惱著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伊莉雅 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 你們也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那孩子已經醒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺... 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個香味是 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}香味？ 是指麵包嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名字？ 我的名字是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}...夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}輝...夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 輝夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是叫輝夜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}輝...夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字叫輝夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 叫輝夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然當時還不知道會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過對麵包感興趣 就是已經有食慾的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼在輝夜恢復之前 我們會送麵包過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以吧 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定又會因為麵包的香味醒過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在幹嘛 你在尋找著什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 快把屋裡的燈關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在是燈火管制啊 你們在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點 立刻關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 聽到了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點關掉 不然的話 我就把門撞開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在幹嘛 現在是燈火管制中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼？ 快點把這個光熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把鳥放出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}船正在靠近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大船嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鳥已經被放出來了 船正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海盜船 難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好 現在不能發光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像在哪我和輝夜見過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海的裡面有著什麼東西嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫里克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像沒見過你 你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}除了自己的名字其他都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克和妮莉絲好像要和古董店的小梅一起去海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是說了財寶 閃閃發光什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}為了下次也能做出幸福的麵包
